content.rendered:
A special relationship develops between two inmates (Miles Teller and Jurnee Smollett) as they grapple with their pasts in a modern penitentiary run by a brilliant visionary (Chris Hemsworth) who experiments with mind-altering drugs on his subjects.

Director: Joseph Kosinski

Writers: George Saunders. Rhett Reese. Paul Wernick

Stars: Chris Hemsworth. Miles Teller. Jurnee Smollett
